narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I feel that I learned a vocabulary that will help me understand modern and contemporary art in any setting. More than just learning about art history I feel comfortable around art, whether we covered it or not, and I am very proud of that. I also feel like my writing significantly improved.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think the course overall was great. If anything could be improved it might be to have more time in breakout rooms, but even still I feel like the course was very engaging.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I feel that I accomplished all of the things I hoped to in this course. I am more well versed in art and feel that I have the tools to understand it, and that is why I would recommend it.

narratives.question_text: The Canvas course site allowed me to identify and access required course materials easily.
